        "URL": "data:text/html;charset=utf-8,%3C!doctype%20html%3E%0A%3Chtml%20lang%3D%22%22%3E%0A%3Chead%3E%0A%20%20%3Cmeta%20charset%3D%22utf-8%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctitle%3EAbout%20the%20Library%3C%2Ftitle%3E%0A%3C%2Fhead%3E%0A%3Cbody%3E%0A%3Cbody%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22aboutcont%22%3E%0A%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22leftlong2%22%20style%3D%22position%3A%20relative%3B%20top%3A70px%22%3E%0A%3Ch2%20style%3D%22padding-left%3A25px%22%3EAbout%3C%2Fh2%3E%0A%3Cp%3EThe%20Library%20of%20Babel%20is%20a%20place%20for%20scholars%20to%20do%20research%2C%20for%20artists%20and%20writers%20to%20seek%20inspiration%2C%20for%20anyone%20with%20curiosity%20or%20a%20sense%20of%20humor%20to%20reflect%20on%20the%20weirdness%20of%20existence%20-%20in%20short%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20like%20any%20other%20library.%20If%20completed%2C%20it%20would%20contain%20every%20possible%20combination%20of%201%2C312%2C000%20characters%2C%20including%20lower%20case%20letters%2C%20space%2C%20comma%2C%20and%20period.%20Thus%2C%20it%20would%20contain%20every%20book%20that%20ever%20has%20been%20written%2C%20and%20every%20book%20that%20ever%20could%20be%20-%20including%20every%20play%2C%20every%20song%2C%20every%20scientific%20paper%2C%20every%20legal%20decision%2C%20every%20constitution%2C%20every%20piece%20of%20scripture%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20At%20present%20it%20contains%20all%20possible%20pages%20of%203200%20characters%2C%20about%2010%3Csup%3E4677%3C%2Fsup%3E%20books.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20imagine%20the%20question%20will%20present%20itself%20in%20some%20visitors%E2%80%99%20minds%20(a%20certain%20amount%20of%20distrust%20of%20the%20virtual%20is%20inevitable)%20I%E2%80%99ll%20head%20off%20any%20doubts%3A%20any%20text%20you%20find%20in%20any%20location%20of%20the%20library%20will%20be%20in%20the%20same%20place%20in%20perpetuity.%20We%20do%20not%20simply%20generate%20and%20store%20books%20as%20they%20are%20requested%20-%20in%20fact%2C%20the%20storage%20demands%20would%20make%20that%20impossible.%20Every%20possible%20permutation%20of%20letters%20is%20accessible%20at%20this%20very%20moment%20in%20one%20of%20the%20library's%20books%2C%20only%20awaiting%20its%20discovery.%20We%20encourage%20those%20who%20find%20strange%20concatenations%20among%20the%20variations%20of%20letters%20to%20write%20about%20their%20discoveries%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FBabelForum%2F%22%20class%3D%22intext%22%3Eforum%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20future%20generations%20may%20benefit%20from%20their%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22rightshort%22%20style%3D%22position%3A%20relative%3B%20top%3A%20158px%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%3Cimg%20class%3D%22about%22%20alt%3D%22the%20amazing%20technicolor%20dream%20goat%22%20title%3D%22The%20Amazing%20Technicolor%20Dream%20Goat%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%3Chr%20style%3D%22clear%3Aboth%3B%20width%3A%2084%25%3B%20position%3A%20relative%3B%20top%3A235px%3B%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22leftshort%22%20style%3D%22position%3A%20relative%3B%20top%3A380px%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Ch2%20style%3D%22position%3A%20relative%3B%20top%3A%20-20px%3B%20left%3A%2025px%22%3EBorges%3C%2Fh2%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cimg%20class%3D%22borges%22%20alt%3D%22photograph%20of%20Borges%20from%201951%22%20title%3D%22Photograph%20of%20Borges%20from%201951%22%20style%3D%22padding-left%3A%2025px%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%20%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22rightlong%22%20style%3D%22position%3A%20relative%3B%20top%3A410px%3B%20left%3A25px%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%20class%3D%22incidental%22%3EJorge%20Luis%20Borges%20is%20without%20doubt%20one%20of%20the%20most%20influential%20and%20innovative%20authors%20of%20the%20twentieth%20century.%20He%20is%20best%20known%20for%20his%20many%20short%20stories%2C%20each%20of%20which%20creates%20a%20sort%20of%20ontological%20thought%20experiment%20in%20a%20few%20brief%20pages.%20He%20wrote%20poetry%20and%20non-fiction%20as%20well%2C%20reflecting%20on%20his%20immense%20knowledge%20of%20world%20literature.%20%3Ca%20class%3D%22intext%22%20target%3D%22_blank%22%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fmaskofreason.files.wordpress.com%2F2011%2F02%2Fthe-library-of-babel-by-jorge-luis-borges.pdf%22%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Library%20of%20Babel%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20(%3Ca%20class%3D%22intext%22%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.literatura.us%2Fborges%2Fbiblioteca.html%22%20target%3D%22_blank%22%3E%E2%80%9CLa%20Biblioteca%20de%20Babel%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E)%20is%20one%20of%20his%20best-known%20and%20most%20loved%20pieces%2C%20from%20the%201941%20collection%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Garden%20of%20Branching%20Paths%3C%2Fi%3E.%20It%20describes%20a%20version%20of%20a%20universal%20library%2C%20containing%20books%20with%20every%20possible%20combination%20of%20410%20pages%20of%20letters%2C%20thus%20containing%20every%20book%20that%20ever%20has%20been%20and%20every%20book%20that%20ever%20could%20be%20written%2C%20drowned%20out%20by%20an%20immense%20quantity%20of%20nonsense.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%20class%3D%22incidental%22%3EBorges%20was%20Argentinian%2C%20and%20aligned%20himself%20with%20many%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20right-leaning%20politicians.%20He%20began%20losing%20his%20sight%20in%20his%20thirties%2C%20and%20was%20appointed%20director%20of%20the%20national%20library%20after%20Per%C3%B3n%E2%80%99s%20exile%2C%20despite%20being%20completely%20blind.%20The%20librarian%20who%20narrates%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Library%20of%20Babel%E2%80%9D%20references%20this%20condition%3A%20%E2%80%9CNow%20that%20my%20eyes%20can%20hardly%20make%20out%20what%20I%20myself%20have%20written%2C%20I%20am%20preparing%20to%20die%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%3Chr%20style%3D%22clear%3Aboth%3B%20width%3A%2084%25%3B%20position%3A%20relative%3B%20top%3A550px%3B%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22leftlong2%22%20style%3D%22position%3A%20relative%3B%20top%3A665px%3B%22%20id%3D%22also%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20launched%20this%20website%2C%20it%20included%20here%20a%20quotation%20from%20Borges'%201939%20essay%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gwern.net%2Fdocs%2Fborges%2F1939-borges-thetotallibrary.pdf%22%20class%3D%22intext%22%20target%3D%22_blank%22%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Total%20Library%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20(%3Ca%20class%3D%22intext%22%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ciudadseva.com%2Ftextos%2Fla-biblioteca-total%22%20target%3D%22_blank%22%3E%E2%80%9CLa%20Biblioteca%20Total%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20%20precursor%20to%20his%20short%20story%2C%20where%20he%20describes%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20universal%20library.%20It%20would%20include%20everything%3A%20the%20minute%20history%20of%20the%20future%2C%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Egyptians%3C%2Fi%3E%20of%20Aeschylus%2C%20the%20precise%20number%20of%20times%20the%20waters%20of%20the%20Ganges%20have%20reflected%20the%20flight%20of%20a%20falcon%2C%20the%20secret%20and%20true%20name%20of%20Rome%2C%20the%20encyclopedia%20Novalis%20would%20have%20written%2C%20Borges'%20dreams%20and%20daydreams%20in%20the%20dawn%20of%20August%2014th%2C%201934%2C%20the%20demonstration%20of%20Pierre%20Fermat's%20theorem%2C%20the%20unwritten%20chapters%20of%20%3Ci%3EEdwin%20Drood%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20those%20same%20chapters%20translated%20into%20the%20language%20of%20the%20Garamantes%2C%20Urizen's%20Books%20of%20Iron%2C%20the%20premature%20epiphanies%20of%20Stephen%20Dedalus%20that%20would%20mean%20nothing%20before%20a%20cycle%20of%20a%20thousand%20years%2C%20the%20gnostic%20gospel%20of%20Basilides%2C%20the%20song%20the%20sirens%20sang%2C%20the%20faithful%20catalogue%20of%20the%20library%2C%20and%20the%20demonstration%20of%20the%20falsehood%20of%20this%20catalog.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20list%20in%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Library%20of%20Babel%E2%80%9D%20adds%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20translation%20of%20every%20book%20into%20every%20language%2C%20the%20interpolations%20of%20every%20book%20into%20all%20books%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20true%20story%20of%20your%20death.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22rightshort%22%20style%3D%22position%3A%20relative%3B%20top%3A665px%3B%22%20id%3D%22thisone%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20said%2C%20this%20quotation%20was%20included%20when%20the%20site%20launched%2C%20but%20unfortunately%20the%20lawyers%20of%20Borges'%20literary%20estate%20asked%20for%20it%20to%20be%20removed.%20His%20estate%20has%20opposed%20every%20genuine%20tribute%20to%20Borges'%20legacy%20out%20of%20the%20misguided%20notion%20that%20they%20will%20profit%20more%20from%20his%20books%20if%20no%20one%20else%20can%20so%20much%20as%20reference%20them.%20For%20a%20sense%20of%20the%20absurd%20lengths%20to%20which%20they%20have%20carried%20this%20quest%2C%20take%20a%20look%20at%20what%20they%20have%20done%20to%20the%20brilliant%20work%20of%20%3Ca%20class%3D%22intext%22%20target%3D%22_blank%22%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fbooks%2Fbooksblog%2F2015%2Fjun%2F25%2Fre-mixing-borges-experiment-not-a-crime-pablo-katchadjian%22%3EPablo%20Katchadjian%2C%20%3Ci%3EEl%20Aleph%20engordado%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20pause%20for%20a%20moment%20to%20honor%20the%20%3Ca%20class%3D%22intext%22%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.digiovanni.co.uk%2Fborges.htm%22%20target%3D%22_blank%22%3Elost%20legacy%20of%20Norman%20Thomas%20di%20Giovanni%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3EBorges%20co-authored%20translations%20of%20the%20majority%20of%20his%20work%20into%20English%20with%20his%20friend%20di%20Giovanni%2C%20with%20whom%20he%20shared%20a%20generous%2050%2F50%20profit-sharing%20agreement.%20After%20Borges'%20death%2C%20the%20publisher%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20his%20estate%2C%20allowed%20these%20works%20to%20go%20out%20of%20print%20and%20commissioned%20the%20Hurley%20translations%20in%20order%20to%20keep%20more%20of%20the%20profits%20for%20themselves.%20He%20was%20also%20prevented%20from%20re-publishing%20his%20work%20or%20publishing%20translations%20he%20wrote%20subsequent%20to%20Borges'%20death.%20We%20can%20at%20least%20take%20solace%20in%20the%20certainty%20that%20Borges'%20legacy%20will%20outlast%20these%20heirs%2C%20despite%20their%20best%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Chr%20style%3D%22clear%3Aboth%3B%20width%3A%2084%25%3B%20position%3A%20relative%3B%20top%3A800px%3B%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22leftlong2%22%20style%3D%22position%3A%20relative%3B%20top%3A%20850px%3B%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Ch2%20style%3D%22position%3A%20relative%3B%20left%3A%2025px%3B%22%3ECreators%3C%2Fh2%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3Elibraryofbabel.info%20is%20the%20creation%20of%20%3Ca%20class%3D%22intext%22%20target%3D%22_blank%22%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fjonathanbasile.com%22%3EJonathan%20Basile%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20working%20with%20the%20help%20of%20my%20friends%20and%20family.%20I%20was%20drawn%20to%20the%20idea%20by%20an%20interest%20in%20literature%20and%20iterability%2C%20which%20I%20suppose%20I%20might%20as%20well%20call%20iterature.%20I%20hope%20you%20find%20the%20library%20aids%20your%20meditations%2C%20and%20please%20let%20me%20know%20via%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FBabelForum%2F%22%20class%3D%22intext%22%3Eforum%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20email%20(jonathan%20%5Bdot%5D%20e%20%5Bdot%5D%20basile%20%5Bat%5D%20gmail%20%5Bdot%5D%20com)%20what%20thoughts%20it%20brings.%20I%20have%20a%20Ph.D.%20in%20Comparative%20Literature%2C%20and%20have%20mostly%20shifted%20my%20focus%20from%20programming%20to%20writing%20about%20the%20life%20sciences%2C%20literature%2C%20and%20philosophy.%20You%20can%20find%20links%20to%20my%20work%20on%20my%20%3Ca%20class%3D%22intext%22%20t